\title{bootstrict: Strict Bootstrap 5.2 Widgets for Shiny}
\description{
\code{bootstrict} re-implements the Bootstrap 5.2 layout, content, forms and
component library as Shiny UI functions. Each widget mirrors the Bootstrap 5
HTML structure one-to-one, theming is delegated to \code{bslib} (so a designer's
SASS variable sheet drops straight in) and interactive components report
their state to the server, with server-side \verb{update_*()} controls.
